17
00:02:01,583 --> 00:02:04,083
- ( rock song playing )

18
00:02:19,625 --> 00:02:21,458
♪ EVERY NIGHT YOU LIGHT ME ♪

19
00:02:21,541 --> 00:02:23,333
♪ WITH YOUR GASOLINE ♪

20
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,166
♪ EVERY TIME I FEEL DELIGHT ♪

21
